ciscoAal5ExtMIB.name: ciscoAal5ExtMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoAal5ExtMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-atm@cisco.com
ciscoAal5ExtMIB.description: This MIB is the RFC 1695 extension for Cisco product. It provides the additional AAL5 performance statistics of a VCC from RFC 1695.

cAal5ExtVccTable.name: cAal5ExtVccTable
cAal5ExtVccTable.description: This table contains AAL5 VCC performance parameters beyond that provided by aal5VccEntry defined in RFC1695 and AAL5 MIB.

cAal5ExtVccEntry.name: cAal5ExtVccEntry
cAal5ExtVccEntry.description: This list contains the additional AAL5 VCC performance parameters beyond that provided by aal5VccEntry defined in RFC1695.

cAal5VccInDroppedPkts.name: cAal5VccInDroppedPkts
cAal5VccInDroppedPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs dropped at the receive side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutDroppedPkts.name: cAal5VccOutDroppedPkts
cAal5VccOutDroppedPkts.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDUs dropped at the transmit side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccInDroppedOctets.name: cAal5VccInDroppedOctets
cAal5VccInDroppedOctets.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDU Octets dropped at the receive side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutDroppedOctets.name: cAal5VccOutDroppedOctets
cAal5VccOutDroppedOctets.description: The number of AAL5 CPCS PDU Octets dropped at the transmit side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccInCells.name: cAal5VccInCells
cAal5VccInCells.description: The number of AAL5 SAR cells received on this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutCells.name: cAal5VccOutCells
cAal5VccOutCells.description: The number of AAL5 SAR cells transmitted on this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccInDroppedCells.name: cAal5VccInDroppedCells
cAal5VccInDroppedCells.description: The number of AAL5 SAR cells dropped at the receive side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

cAal5VccOutDroppedCells.name: cAal5VccOutDroppedCells
cAal5VccOutDroppedCells.description: The number of AAL5 SAR cells dropped at the transmit side of this AAL5 VCC at the interface associated with an AAL5 entity.

ciscoAAL5ExtMIBCompliance.name: ciscoAAL5ExtMIBCompliance
ciscoAAL5ExtMIBCompliance.description: The compliance statement for entities which implement this Cisco AAL5 EXT MIB.

ciscoAal5ExtMIBGroup.name: ciscoAal5ExtMIBGroup
ciscoAal5ExtMIBGroup.description: A collection of objects providing these extra AAL5 interface related statistics.
